Class AnalyticsSession

java.lang.Object
  com.appglu.AnalyticsSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AnalyticsSession
extends Object
implements Serializable

Represents a session of application usage. From the time the user has opened the app to the time it closes it.
A session can contain parameters and events and is used to collect mobile app usage statistics.

Since:
1.0.0
